#### How do I register?

You need to register as a user on [registration application](http://app.euruko2009.org) and then go to the _"Pay"_ section. Follow the steps from there to select the event and pay through PayPal, or credit card.

Being registered on the application doesn'tn imply you have a seat, only when your payment has been received, your seat will be reserved for you.

